
### Privacy Policy for Sterix Bot  

Sterix Bot ("the Bot") is committed to protecting your privacy. This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you interact with our services on Discord.  

#### Data Collection  
Sterix Bot collects limited data necessary to provide functionality and enhance your experience. The data collected includes:  
- User IDs  
- Guild IDs  
- Command usage logs  
- Messages for specific features (temporary storage only)  

We do not collect sensitive personal information.  

#### Data Usage  
The data collected is used for:  
- Responding to commands and processing requests  
- Enhancing bot features and performance  
- Debugging and resolving issues  

#### Data Sharing  
Sterix Bot does not share your data with third parties unless required by law or necessary to protect the safety of users and the integrity of our services.  

#### Data Storage and Security  
- Collected data is stored securely and is accessible only to authorized personnel.  
- Data related to temporary operations is automatically deleted after completion.  

#### User Rights  
You have the right to request data deletion or obtain details about the data we hold about you. Contact us through the support server for assistance: [Sterix Support Server](https://discord.gg/V2FvH3YJSm).  

#### Updates to the Policy  
This privacy policy may be updated periodically. Any significant changes will be communicated through the support server.  

By using Sterix Bot, you agree to the terms outlined in this privacy policy.  

